# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` for local `wrangler dev`.
# Values here are for documentation only - never commit real secrets.
#
# Minimal template: no variables are required for the current codebase (health
# route only). When you add secrets:
# 1. Uncomment `secrets.required` in `wrangler.jsonc` (same secret names).
# 2. Add matching keys here (only listed names are loaded once `secrets` is defined).
# 3. Deploy: `wrangler secret put EXAMPLE_SECRET --env staging` (repeat per env).
#
# EXAMPLE_SECRET="replace-me"
